At a YC event last week Brian Chesky gave a talk that everyone whowas there will remember. Most founders I talked to afterward saidit was the best they'd ever heard. Ron Conway, for the first timein his life, forgot to take notes. I'm not going to try to reproduceit here. Instead I want to talk about a question it raised.

